beautiful and peaceful religion

255
00:11:12,814 --> 00:11:15,248
look like a bunch
of bloodthirsty barbarians.

256
00:11:15,250 --> 00:11:16,215
You love that movie.

257
00:11:16,217 --> 00:11:18,985
Yeah, it's pretty great.

258
00:11:21,588 --> 00:11:24,457
I'm surprised to see you
suddenly get religious.

259
00:11:24,459 --> 00:11:25,725
Why?

260
00:11:25,727 --> 00:11:28,494
Well, because I've known you
for ten years

261
00:11:28,496 --> 00:11:30,196
and you've never gone to temple,

262
00:11:30,198 --> 00:11:31,997
you never talked
about believing in God,

263
00:11:31,999 --> 00:11:36,268
