for attacking quantum theory

281
00:12:15,142 --> 00:12:17,509
on the grounds
that “God does not play dice

282
00:12:17,511 --> 00:12:18,844
with the universe.”
Well, of course

283
00:12:18,846 --> 00:12:22,648
he believed in God--
he slept with Marilyn Monroe.

284
00:12:22,650 --> 00:12:24,449
Actually
there's no proof of that.

285
00:12:24,451 --> 00:12:27,185
You believe in your religion,
I'll believe in mine.

286
00:12:29,923 --> 00:12:31,490
How's it going
in there?

287
00:12:31,492 --> 00:12:32,492
Eh.

288
00:12:32,493 --> 00:12:35,360
Not really a great outfit
for work,

289
00:12:35,362 --> 00:12:39,898
unless something opens up in
the hookers and whores division.

290
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:42,868
Hey, can I ask you something?
Sure.

291
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:45,637
Do I really force you
to do things you don't want to?

292
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:47,572
Yeah, but it's okay.

293
00:12:47,574 --> 00:12:48,807
How is it okay?

294
00:12:48,809 --> 00:12:51,209
I promised myself,
if I ever got friends,

295
00:12:51,211 --> 00:12:53,445
I'd do whatever they said.

296
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:57,716
