before a cult did.

297
00:12:57,718 --> 00:13:00,552
Well, you know,
that was a long time ago.

298
00:13:00,554 --> 00:13:03,321
You're a different woman now.
You're smart,

299
00:13:03,323 --> 00:13:06,024
