348
00:15:15,821 --> 00:15:17,954
I'm not upset.

349
00:15:17,956 --> 00:15:23,226
I'm just imagining a world
without my best friend in it.

350
00:15:24,328 --> 00:15:25,562
Sheldon.

351
00:15:25,564 --> 00:15:26,530
It's okay.

352
00:15:26,532 --> 00:15:29,366
