353
00:15:29,368 --> 00:15:32,202
I'm just talking
about living across the hall.

354
00:15:32,204 --> 00:15:33,470
I understand.

355
00:15:33,472 --> 00:15:36,072
Either way,
I want you to know that...

356
00:15:36,074 --> 00:15:38,208
I'm aware of how difficult
I can be.

