00:16:32,996 --> 00:16:34,797
Okay.

375
00:16:34,799 --> 00:16:36,766
When I'm not home.

376
00:16:37,601 --> 00:16:39,869
You got it.

377
00:16:40,737 --> 00:16:42,605
There we go,

378
00:16:42,607 --> 00:16:45,308
